---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Notice - Lewisham Your Party">
    <main class="min-h-screen bg-yp-cream text-yp-slate p-8 md:p-16 pt-0 md:pt-0">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <a href="/" class="inline-block mb-8 text-yp-red font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:underline">
                &larr; Back to Home
            </a>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 md:p-12 shadow-xl border-t-8 border-yp-red mb-20">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading uppercase tracking-tighter mb-6">Privacy Notice</h1>
            
            <div class="space-y-6 text-lg opacity-90">
                <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 13 March 2026</p>

                <p>This privacy notice explains how the Lewisham branch of Your Party (currently operating as a grassroots organizing group) collects, uses, and protects your personal information. Because we are a local volunteer-run group, our data collection is minimal and focused entirely on local organizing.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">Who We Are</h2>
                <p>We are the local organizing committee for Lewisham Your Party. Please note that while we campaign for Your Party, we are currently a grassroots proto-branch.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">How We Collect Your Data</h2>
                <p>We only collect personal data when you voluntarily provide it to us by filling out the contact or signup forms on our website. The data we collect currently includes:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Email Address</li>
                    <li>Any other information you volunteer in our consent forms</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">What We Use Your Data For</h2>
                <p>We rely on your consent and our legitimate interest as a political movement to use your data to:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Email you updates about local Lewisham campaigns and news.</li>
                    <li>Invite you to local meetings, street stalls, and events.</li>
                    <li>Coordinate volunteer efforts.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">Who We Share Your Data With</h2>
                <p>We <strong>never</strong> sell your data or share it with data brokers. Because our website uses a lean, modern architecture, your data is only processed by secure third-party tools that help us route your messages to our volunteer team:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Web3Forms:</strong> securely captures your form submissions and emails them to us.</li>
                    <li><strong>Cloudflare:</strong> provides secure hosting and bot-protection for our website.</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="italic text-sm mt-4">Note: Once our branch is officially integrated with the central Your Party organization, your data may be securely migrated to the national party's database. We will notify you before this happens.</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mt-8">Your Rights</h2>
                <p>Under UK data protection law, you have the right to ask what data we hold about you, request that we correct or delete it, or withdraw your consent for us to contact you at any time. To exercise these rights, please reply to any of our organizer emails.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>